merge_before_transcript:
rachel: Shh-shh-shh! The guys don’t know yet do they?
monica: No! Joey and Ross don’t know anything and Chandler still thinks that Phoebe’s pregnant.
phoebe_transcript: Yeah that’s right Chandler does still think I’m pregnant. He hasn’t asked me how I’m feeling or offered to carry my bags. Boy, I feel bad for the woman who ends up with him. (Monica looks at her.) After you of course.
